{"tid":2049623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★帛金有公價也有「最低消費」 最少$501？!!","createTime":"2020-06-03T14:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T18:32:09.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b1766d58f3ca0f588b6301d47e0669ff53cc67c6","tid":2049623,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:43:02.000Z","msg":"一份帛金，本為聊表思念故人的心意，現在竟然也有「最低消費」？有打工仔反映，近日驚悉做帛金原來也有「公價」，最少要封501元才算體面，令人瞠目結舌。但有殯儀業人士表示，帛金絕無公價，只需隨心意去做即可。<br />\n<br />\n追思故人的喪禮，竟也變成糾紛來源？有網民在討論區反映，近日得悉帛金也有公價，頓感譁然。帖文指︰「有同事跟我說現在百物騰貴，做帛金最基本要畀501元。我都覺得奇怪，難道封帛金不是要看交情和關係嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n帖文一出，即引來近萬人點擊。不少網民指，若帛金也有公價，等同「發死人財」。有網民認為，做帛金要看個人能力及交情，直言若喪主對帛金感到不滿意，應反省自身，而非怪別人「畀得少」。有人感嘆，自幼受母訓，對於紅白二事也不應計較金額，賓客是「有心才來」，嘆世人變得太功利。<br />\n<br />\n金額視乎能力與交情<br />\n<br />\n有網民就分享，遇上同事家中有喪事，「畀與不畀帛金」頓成大難題，「成間公司有400人，根本不知那同事是誰，但秘書就傳來公文袋叫同事夾帛金，還要在袋面寫明自己做了多少錢，好老套。」有過來人亦身同感受，直言數年前奔喪時，被要求做帛金要「301元起價」；有人更曾被怪責帛金「封得少」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民則指，雖然未曾要求做指定金額，但有親友過身時，家中長輩要求「一人送一個花牌」，幸好親屬設靈的地方寬敞，否則放完花牌都無位行。有人建議，做帛金時除了考慮交情，也要視乎死者的年齡而定，「如果英年早逝，家中尚有遺孤，一般會做多些︰如高齡辭世的，做101元加花牌已夠體面。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2023544/%E5%B8%9B%E9%87%91%E6%9C%89%E5%85%AC%E5%83%B9%20%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%91$501%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2023544%2F%25E5%25B8%259B%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2583%25B9%2520%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25B0%2591%24501%25EF%25BC%259F&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=c695af46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2023544/%E5%B8%9B%E9%87%91%E6%9C%89%E5%85%AC%E5%83%B9%20%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%91$501%EF%BC%9F</a>"},{"pid":"332ea01352faa5c59382abf25b0a7c47738666ce","tid":2049623,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03a515d41245dbb0ece27cbe81156b8ef4578a3","tid":2049623,"uid":201604,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"嫌少咪下次補返"},{"pid":"c6cb64aa5115890b7f004ea66cea26f448525313","tid":2049623,"uid":103759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:43:56.000Z","msg":"連登-&gt;公海-&gt;連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321f3915f15a38c984399236930199d39b10d4e6","tid":2049623,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6cb64aa5115890b7f004ea66cea26f448525313","tid":2049623,"uid":103759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:43:56.000Z","msg":"連登-&gt;公海-&gt;連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"154834730e631ad86ef3bd427c7d8e08871158fe","tid":2049623,"uid":356254,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:45:36.000Z","msg":"問ming仔 會清楚d"},{"pid":"6ea7ac20fc225c1ce63b4c97187e6ea30497bee1","tid":2049623,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6cb64aa5115890b7f004ea66cea26f448525313",